lead_paragraph: Hernan Perez hit a two-run homer, singled and scored the go-ahead run in the sixth, Zach Davies pitched 6 1/3 innings and the Milwaukee Brewers beat the Arizona Diamondbacks 6-4 on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Perez, Davies Lead Brewers to 6-4 Win Over Diamondbacks
